verbose_text: Overexpression of miR-21, miR-27a, miR-34, miR-34a, miR-146a, miR-155, miR-196a, miR-203, and miR-221 was detected, with miR-21, miR-27a, miR-34, miR-34a, and miR-196a being particularly highly expressed in squamous cell carcinoma of the cervix [XREF_BIBR].
